Mother’s Day vibes with my two favorite people❤️

I just want to say, to all mothers out there creating content and taking care of their homes, all respect to you. We all know it takes a few people to help out every once in a while to raise a baby, however being far away from our family does make it a lot harder to keep up our day-to-day content. Behind the scenes it takes a lot of time and effort to get dressed, do your makeup, hair and at the same time take care of your baby's needs. Yes, it’s a lot of work but we mothers make it all worth it in the end. 

Ps: A button had to get re-sowed, an earring had to get glued back together, our baby had to get fed two times, and a toe got sprained 😂 I must add that it took us at least five hours but thank God the pictures came out beautiful. I hope you guys enjoy them as much as we love creating them.
